Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:51.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次我想请大家去海水浴  附带温泉一宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,去海边吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个能遮的住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,这位客人  您想买什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,小…小鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你喜欢这样的啊  朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你太色了  朝仓纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,被说中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,喂  不要耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:19.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,唉  完全被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:25.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这两年的后勤部队可不是白做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:33.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,被你全方位看了个够的这两年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果考关于朝仓君的题目的话  我能得不错的分数哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,能高过一般人不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和音梦约好了见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  去享受你们两个人的时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,替我向音梦问好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,出局…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要“非常草莓”和“卷花焦糖”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,买双份的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你迟到的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦你要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:29.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  有个地方想和哥哥一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,再来一个“薄荷之吻”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,三份吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,橡…橡皮艇(gomu booto)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:59.20,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：[尻取り]（接龙）是将前一个日语单词的最后一个发音做为开始，由下一个人继续\N说一个词，以此类推。由于和中文发音不一样，看翻译后的中文是看不明白的，所以把每\N个日语的读音用罗马字写了出来，大家自己注意看下就明白了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,橡皮艇的‘to’
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,是‘to’吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:57.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,是关于海的接龙游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以要用和海有关的来接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,“土用波”(doyounami)行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.23,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：立秋前18天前后，由于台风而引起的洋面上的大浪。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,mi… 泳衣(mizugi)！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,mizugi的‘gi’？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:15.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,gi… 只放卷心菜的炒面(yakisoba)！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:23.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}{\an8}{\pos(352,10)}注释：キャベツ（卷心菜）的第一个发音是“ki”，虽然不是“gi”，不过是“gi”的清\N　　　音。也算蒙混过去了。所以下边纯一说“还算OK”。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:21.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,海之家的炒面  几乎不加什么料的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点夸张不过还算OK  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,下面轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,是‘ba’啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:39.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,每幢样子都不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:47.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,哇  有几幢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,看  选对地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢  眼光不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐  别想接龙的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,香草冰激凌(baniraaisu)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:08.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,真子  下一个是‘su’哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,‘su’啊…su…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:12.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,早结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,西瓜(suika)啊！  西瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,衫并！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临西洋风格小屋‘我的家’
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你果然先来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说你怎么不来集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,天很热吧  进来喝点冰豆浆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要自己装出一副主人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了  不要计较这些小事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点换衣服去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,里边是什么样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我给朝仓你预备了特别房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,特别房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是烤鱼的烤炉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:03.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是Mantelpiece  是北欧的暖炉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在是夏天  所以不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  这个也可以拿来烤鱼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:16.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,看啊看啊  海好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:19.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们马上就可以去游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,登记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,无聊的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,这哪里是特别房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:36.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是能充分体验自然的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,能净化被现代文明所污染的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,是治疗的空间  恢复之所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是很特别很高级吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚你的脸都红了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,海豚  完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:12.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,要穿上哥哥选的泳衣  还是有点害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  肯定合适你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想让哥哥第一个看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:43.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,不好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有这事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的  没错  YES！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,第一次穿的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:23.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,看  是用香蕉皮做的新材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,尺寸合适的只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:55.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,是夏娃！ 这泳衣简直就是为了让水越姐穿而诞生的～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎？  这么说小鸟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的  切的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,阿环好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:02.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是爱丽丝想吃的烤鱿鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像和想象中的大不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  做的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,老师  这个很有艺术感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,下一部作品是以这个城堡为舞台吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,哼  要是海水是甜的那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:33.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚你知道为什么海水又咸又涩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:42.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为  伤心欲绝的少女的眼泪流到海里的缘故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:45.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,少女的眼泪？  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:49.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,十分诗情画意又很甜蜜的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:53.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,故事？  这是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦？  老师  你开玩笑的本领也是一流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:57.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的贝壳啊  音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:20.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的泳衣  很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起拣贝壳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:30.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,下面我们玩计分的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很笨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:05.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,来海边玩竟然会忘记泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得好好谢谢你  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是这次聚会的主要目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你给我很多帮助  为我做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上叫醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,为我打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,烫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有替我猜考题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:33.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了  还有一次洗澡某人忘记给我烧热水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:42.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,这两年尽是给小鸟你们添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:08.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的很有趣  这两年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该去准备烧烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:28.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:42.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在还…对朝仓君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:55.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,呃…各位  今天阳光明媚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家百忙之中  能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓  你被校长幽灵附身了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,会贫血的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  开场白不要这么长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,那太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:23.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,各位  谢谢大家在我不在的这两年里照顾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,能够有今天的我全都是托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  你也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:30.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,严重妻管严啊  朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,衫并
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,玩了这么久了  感觉有多少都能吃得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是很好吃呢  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:57.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  和大家一起什么都觉得好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:58.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,要注意营养均衡  蔬菜也要多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:02.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,想逃避吃蔬菜吗  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:11.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是不是  只是去拿点肉过来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,回来后我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:24.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  我不在的两年你一直这样为哥哥着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  大概就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,那真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥他有没有耍性子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  一点也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也得向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢朝仓君才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  我也是喜欢朝仓才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,开…开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…我也喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,美春我最喜欢音梦前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,第二位是香蕉  第三四…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:12.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然排名不靠前但我很喜欢朝仓前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:16.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢朝仓君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？  在说我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:25.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  正在谈论朝仓君大受欢迎的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我也得参战才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:33.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓  我爱你  朝仓啊  亲一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,说出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,得把这份心…收起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:23.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为和纯一在一起的小鸟看起来是那么幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,露馅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:37.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…非常喜欢朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:55.60,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,香波弄到眼睛里去了好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐坐这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们交班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,晒的好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,很红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:10.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为检查身体时被你看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:21.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,夏天到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:22.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:27.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,今年夏天得补回和朝仓君的两年空白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,哇  好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,给  拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,满地石头真难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还没睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:59.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实我有重要的事情和你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,衫并
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,都是梦话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…  小鸟她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经…  不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,少女的眼泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:26.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,明明喜欢纯一  为什么不说实话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,对小鸟而言那是幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:38.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,月光下波光鳞鳞的海面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:18.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,在远处窃窃私语的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,被夏天的气息所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:27.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,轻轻关闭了的梦之门  再次慢慢打开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的心却如此平静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,充满悲伤的回忆  何时才能变得幸福呢？
